node.text:
Smelll proof bags are the gift to give! 🎅🏽🎄@SkunkBags provides luxurious, beautifully crafted bags that come in options from fanny packs and small carrying cases all the way to book bags and full sized luggage with wheels.  Skunk Bags have created a scientific formula that holds the smell in the bag so you aren't stanking up the place with your entire stash.
Visit http://SkunkBags.com and use code "Chong" at checkout for 15% off and make sure to follow them on Instagram @skunkbags 🎁
